description._content: Catalog #: 09_01239 Title: H. Murray Gibson Special Collection Photo Additional Information: Group standing in front of Greyhound buses in depot. Four drivers identified as 'Williams, Adams, H. Murray Gibson and Hopkins', H. Murray Gibson was a bus driver for the Greyhound bus company. He was also an aviation enthusiast who took flying lessons throughout the 1930s. Corporation Name: Greyhound Lines, Inc Tags: H.
